# Turorial
this commit will help you how ti install and load mod for android
# Install app
simply go to [release](https://github.com/hoomanfish-f5/ruined-balatro/releases)
and download latest build version
go to file manager and click apk files (disable play protect if has issue)
# Load Mods
to make mods works i recomended to use [Material Files](https://github.com/zhanghai/materialfiles)
run the game once to get folder
open Material Files and click hamburger on left and select "Add Storage"  
then click "External storage"
make sure offical android files app must needed
then click hamburger on left and select app
then click the folder maned "ASET" or "Mods"
and set folder
now you can load mod property.
